    <h2 {...{
      "id": "configuration"
    }}>{`Configuration`}</h2>
    <p>{`Some frameworks like `}<strong parentName="p">{`Symfony`}</strong>{` are already providing scripts for preloading the entire code base to improve the performance.`}</p>
    <ol>
      <li parentName="ol">{`Open the `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`php.ini`}</inlineCode>{` of your `}<strong parentName="li">{`PHP Version`}</strong>{`:`}</li>
