`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`By default, all `}<strong parentName="p">{`PHP Versions`}</strong>{` on CloudPanel have a default PHP-FPM Pool running as user `}<strong parentName="p">{`clp`}</strong>{` and group `}<strong parentName="p">{`clp`}</strong>{`.`}</p>
